Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abyss Razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Starting now, I will give your eye\Na better purpose.}Từ giờ ta sẽ cho đôi mắt của\N ngươi có vai trò hữu dụng hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Starting today, you are my tool.}Bắt đầu từ hôm nay sẽ là công cụ của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Theo ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Lord Abel.}Ngài Abel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Around the time when Mash and the gang\Nwere victorious over Magia Lupus...}{\i0}Trong lúc Mash và đồng bọn vừa\N đánh thắng Magia Lupus...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I wonder how Mash is doing now.}Mash nó đang làm gì nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I hope people didn't find out he can't\Nuse magic and make a big deal out of it.}Hi vọng không ai phát hiện ra nó không có phép thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm in trouble if he doesn't do his best\Nto become Divine Visionary.}Tôi cũng sẽ gặp rắc rối nếu nó\N không trở thành Thánh nhân đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's part of my future planning, after all.}Tất cả đều vì tương lai của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You don't need to work?}Cậu không cần đi làm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Công việc của tôi là chờ đợi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Time on screen is important.}Việc quan trọng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's important.}Phải, quan trọng lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You want some more tea?}Thêm tách trà nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Allow me to regale it again.}{\i0}Để tôi nói lại lần nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This story is where Mash Burnedead with\Nno magical powers enters Easton Magic Academy,}{\i0}Đây là câu chuyện về kẻ không phép thuật \NMash Burnedead vào học viện ma pháp Easton.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Hip, hip, hooray!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and becomes Divine Visionary...}{\i0}Và trở thành Thánh nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wait, they're still getting carried away!}{\i0}Cơ mà con đường vẫn còn dài lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Main character! Main character!\NMain character! Main character!}Nhân vật chính! {Main character! Main character!\NMain character! Main character!}Nhân vật chính! {Main character! Main character!\NMain character! Main character!}Nhân vật chính! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Heroine! Heroine! I am heroine!}Nữ chính! {Heroine! Heroine! I am heroine!}Nữ chính! {Heroine! Heroine! I am heroine!}Nữ chính! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You are hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah!}Yê!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hip, hip, hooray!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hip, hip, hooray!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{How long are they going to do that?}{\i0}Bọn nó định làm đến khi nào nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{How long are they doing that?}Sao làm hoài vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, is it all right if I go to the bathroom?}Khoan, tôi đi vệ sinh cái.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He must’ve been holding it all this time.}{\i0}Hẳn là nhịn dữ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Anyway, guess that's over.}Cơ mà kết thúc rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All the students that were turned into puppets\Nare back to normal now.}Mấy học sinh cũng trở lại bình thường rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But this school\Nis such a hive of lawlessness.}Nhưng ngôi trường này vô phép quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And that thrill accelerates romance.}Và cả lãng mạn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{By the way, where is that handsome punk?\NDid he lose or something?}Cơ mà thằng khốn đẹp trai đâu? Thua à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't think Lance would lose.}Tớ không nghĩ Lance có thể thua đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? That was really fast...}Ủa? Nhanh thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Who are you?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Get lost.}Biến.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Ow! What the hell d'ya...}Mày là thằng nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's with the wounds?\NDid you lose against someone?}Vết thương này là sao? Ngươi thua ai à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You couldn't even rise\Nto the top of this school.}Mỗi việc đứng đầu ngôi trường cũng không làm được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're pretty pathetic.}Thảm hại.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But I do appreciate you...}Nhưng ta cũng cảm ơn ngươi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{for giving us intel\Nabout Headmaster Wahlberg.}vì đã thông tin về lão hiệu trưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My hands are moving on their own.}{\i0}Tay ta tự di chuyển...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You didn't find the one\Nwe're searching for though.}Nhưng ngươi không tìm được kẻ bọn ta cần.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But it turns out that\Nwe don't need you anymore.}Thế nên cũng không cần ngươi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We don’t need—}Bọn ta không cần--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We can all party with orange juice\Nand cream puffs.}Chúng ta có thể tổ chức tiệc su kem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's with that brat\Nwho can't read the room?}{\i0}Thằng nhãi nào có duyên vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? It kinda feels like...}Ủa? Cảm giác như là...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mash, this is bad. We're in no mood\Nfor stuff like that right now.}Mash, nguy cấp rồi. Giờ không phải lúc tấu hài đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait, where did you get\Nthose cream puffs from?}Mà cậu lấy thứ đó ở đâu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.15,Default,On-screen text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SPLCK SPLCK SPLCK SPLCK SPLCK}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Was it coincidence!?}{\i0}Ngẫu nhiên à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Was it intentional?}{\i0}Hay cố ý?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um, sorry to bother you, but we were gonna\Neat those, so could you give them back?}Xin lỗi vì làm phiền, nhưng bọn này muốn\N ăn nó nên là trả lại được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's going to eat cream puffs in that state?}{\i0}Nó vẫn còn muốn ăn su kem à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Shock!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.93,Default,On-screen text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SHOCK}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Insolent boy.}Thằng hỗn láo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What is this headache?}{\i0}Cái cơn đau đầu này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is it resonance?}{\i0}Cộng hưởng?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But I didn't have this headache\Nwhen I arrived.}{\i0}Nhưng từ lúc đến đây mình chưa từng bị...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It can't possibly be\Nthis guy that just came in?}{\i0}Không lẽ từ lúc nó xuất hiện?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Really, him?}{\i0}Là nó hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is this guy\Nthe one we've been searching for?}{\i0}Đây là kẻ bọn ta đang tìm kiếm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, fine.}Mà thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{First, to finish what I came here for.}Đầu tiên, hoàn thành mục đích trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Killing Abel as planned!}Giết Abel như kế hoạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's useless.}Vô ích.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Can’t you see? You’re no match...}Khoảng cách thực lực quá lớn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{for someone like me.}Ngươi không có cửa với ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Now die.}Chết đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mask Guy.}Ông anh mặt nạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry, Mash.}Xin lỗi Mash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It looks like I won't be able...\Nto eat cream puffs with you.}Có vẻ tôi không thể ăn su kem cùng cậu được rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Take this.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A magic handkerchief.}Khăn tay ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My attack was not fatal?}{\i0}Đòn tấn công của ta không gây tử vong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That Mushroom Head threw a rock at me\Nright before my spell to alter the trajectory.}{\i0}Thằng đầu nấm đó ném viên đá vào\N làm thay đổi quỹ đạo thần chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So this guy really is...}{\i0}Quả nhiên là nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Abel's lapdog, huh? How admirable.}Con chó của Abel à? Ngưỡng mộ ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that your gratitude for being adopted\Ndespite being an eyesore of society?}Tỏ lòng biết ơn vì được hắn nhận nuôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's really revolting.}Thật đáng kinh tởm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's stomping the ground?}{\i0}Nó giẫm chân xuống sàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He caught it.}Hắn bắt được sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Amazing!}Đỉnh quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey. You're quite the rebel.}Này này, mày đang tuổi nổi loạn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I won't hesitate to kill you too!}Tao sẽ giết luôn cả mày.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? Why are you licking a rock?}Hả? Sao thằng này lại liếm hòn đá?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you in that kind of phase?}Đang trong giai đoạn đó hả ông anh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Anyway...}Mà thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I've gotta get Mask Guy to an infirmary.}Tôi phải đưa anh mặt nạ đến bệnh xá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Try to stop me\Nand I'll beat the stuffing out of you.}Nếu dám cản đường thì đừng trách.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Beat the stuffing outta me, huh?}Định đánh bại ta à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right.}Được đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{How does 30 minutes sound for how long\Nhe has before he's beyond help?}Nó chỉ có thể chịu được 30 phút nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Will you be able to save him?}Liệu ngươi có thể cứu được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought you were going\Nto beat the stuffing outta me?}Tưởng đòi đập ta cho ra bã mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Or are you all talk?}Hay võ mồm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He can't win.}{\i0}Cậu ta không thể thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's too big of a gap\Nin the qualities they were born with.}{\i0}Khoảng cách sức mạnh quá lớn từ lúc sinh ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Qualities.}{\i0}Khoảng cách?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:10:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mother often said to me it was only\Nby chance that we were born privileged.}{\i0}Mẹ thường hay nói ta sinh ra \Nchỉ tình cờ được may mắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Birthright, talent, appearance.}{\i0}Toả sáng, tài năng, vẻ bề ngoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It was chance that bestowed\Nthose advantages on people.}{\i0}Những kẻ được ban tặng đều là may mắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's why...}{\i0}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't zone out now, Abel!}Đừng ngẩn ngơ nữa, Abel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Carborain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's impossible.}{\i0}Không thể đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We are unquestionably inferior.}Chúng ta không thể chống lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We cannot win against him.}Không thể thắng hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Abyss was a fool.}Abyss thật ngu ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He didn't have to make an effort\Nto protect me at all.}Cậu không cần phải bảo vệ cho ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I think he was happy.}Tôi nghĩ anh ấy đã rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He was all alone for the longest time.}Vì đã luôn cô đơn lẻ loi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It was so tough for him to keep living.}Thật khó khăn để sống tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And that's why I think\Nhe was happy that you needed him.}Và đó là lý do anh ấy thấy vui vì được anh sử dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought about how I would feel\Nif I was in a similar situation.}Tôi cũng sẽ vui nếu đặt trong vị trí đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So...}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm going to save him.}Tôi sẽ cứu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I think Mask Guy\Nwants to eat cream puffs, too.}Tôi nghĩ mặt nạ muốn ăn bánh su kem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It was only by chance\Nthat we were born privileged.}{\i0}Chúng ta sinh ra chỉ tình cờ được may mắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Birthright, talent, appearance.\NThey're mere coincidences.}{\i0}Toả sáng, tài năng, vẻ bề ngoài, tất cả đều là trùng hợp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's why, Abel...}{\i0}Thế nên Abel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Learn to put yourself in another's position.}{\i0}Hãy học cách đứng vào vị trí của người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you can do that...}{\i0}Nếu làm thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You will become\Njust a little bit kinder to others.}{\i0}Con sẽ trở nên dịu dàng với mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes, just a little... kinder to others.}{\i0}Phải... dần dần sẽ trở nên... dịu dàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just accept it!}Chấp nhận đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Carborain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{L-Lord Abel...}N-Ngài Abel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's the Eye of the Devil! Run!}{\i0}Quỷ nhãn kìa! Chạy mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Stay away from me!}{\i0}Tránh xa ta ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I wish I didn't give birth to you!}{\i0}Ước gì mày chưa từng được sinh ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sorry.\NI'm sorry I was ever born.}{\i0}Xin lỗi vì con được sinh ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I've heard you possess the Eye of the Devil?}Ta nghe nói ngươi có Quỷ nhãn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.\NI'll be careful not to make eye contact.}Xin lỗi. Tôi sẽ cẩn thận hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There's no need to hide it.}Không cần phải giấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Will you use that eye for my sake?}Ngươi có thể sử dụng nó vì ta chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can't possibly do that.}Tôi không thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because of this eye,\Neveryone will avoid you as well.}Vì đôi mắt này mà mọi người sẽ tránh né cậu đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That doesn't matter to me.}Không quan tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Starting now,\NI will give your eye a better purpose.}Từ bây giờ, ta sẽ cho đôi mắt đó mục đích sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Starting today, you are my tool.}Từ hôm nay, ngươi là công cụ của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Come along.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{P-Please...}L-Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{P-Please... run while... you can...}Hãy chạy... ngay đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Always so noble.}{\i0}Thật đẹp đẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mother.}{\i0}Mẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And Abyss.}{\i0}Và Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Carborain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that all you can manage?}Chỉ thế thôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You poor, pitiful, pathetic, miserable thing!}Tội nghiệp, thảm hại, khốn khổ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hurry up, or you'll run out of time!}Nhanh lên, sắp hết giờ rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is bad.}{\i0}Tệ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not only are those carbon-nugget things\Nrock-solid, but there's too many of them.}{\i0}Cục than dạng rắn đó không chỉ\N cứng mà còn quá nhiều nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mash is slowly pushing forward,\Nbut he doesn't have enough time to get up close.}{\i0}Mash đang từ từ nhích lên nhưng \Nkhông thể áp sát nhanh chóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But then, if I headed over to help Mash,\Nthe two left here will be in danger.}{\i0}Nhưng nếu đến giúp Mash thì\N hai người này sẽ gặp nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't move from here.}{\i0}Mình không thể hành động!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm getting bored of this.}Ta chán rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Carbo Heavy Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What? A higher-ranked version!?}{\i0}Cái gì? Phiên bản cao cấp hơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh no. It's getting even more hopeless\Nto make it in time.}{\i0}Không ổn. Lại gần bây giờ là không thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Should I go assist him? Damn it.}{\i0}Có nên ra đó không? Mẹ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The strong take from the weak,\Nand that's their right.}Kẻ mạnh cướp của kẻ yếu. Đó là quy luật.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The weak oppose the strong,\Nand that's also their right.}Kẻ yếu chống lại kẻ mạnh, đó là quyền của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's the meaning of this, Abel?}Vậy là sao Abel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm seeing for myself what is righteous,}Ta đang làm việc mình cho là đúng,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{with my own hands.}bằng đôi tay này.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hmph. I see.}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Carbo Heavy Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Too bad.}Đáng tiếc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can't win with this kind of magic...}Ngươi sẽ không thể thắng với cái ma thuật...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey there.}Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're the first to break through\Nmy rigid epidermis.}Ngươi là kẻ đầu tiên phá được lớp bảo vệ của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Even though I was caught off guard.}Cơ mà ta có hơi bất cẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What magic did you use?}Ngươi dùng ma thuật gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm asking you what your personal magic is.}Ta hỏi Ma pháp cố hữu của ngươi là gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh... Um...}Hả? À...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Power!?}{\i0}Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Such magic exists!?}{\i0}Có thể loại ma thuật đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hmph. So you're refusing to answer me.}Ngươi không trả lời à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kệ đi.{Whatever.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{the Spellflection Mirror!}Gương thần!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A powerful magical item that reflects\Nany and every spell cast its way!}Vật phẩm ma thuật sẽ phản lại mọi câu thần chú?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And the stronger the spell,\Nthe more fearsome the mirror makes it!}Thần chú càng mạnh thì chiếc gương càng đáng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The most feared magical item\Nthat makes every magic user cower in terror.}Thứ vật phẩm khiến mọi ma thuật sư sợ đái ra máu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought the Bureau of Magic\Nwas guarding it. So why...}Cứ tưởng nó đang được Cục Ma pháp giữ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mash, don't!}Mash, dừng lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We magic users don't stand a chance\Nagainst that thing!}Những kẻ sử dụng ma thuật \Nnhư chúng ta không thể thắng đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It'll send your spells right back at you!}Nó sẽ phản lại mọi thần chú!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{One mistake and you're as good as dead!}Chỉ sai một li là đi luôn xuống suối vàng đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you're gonna beat it,\Nyou have to do it without using magic.}{\i0}Nếu muốn đánh bại nó thì chỉ còn cách đánh chay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But such a feat...}Nhưng mà chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's because you got in my way.}Vì ngươi dám cản trở ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll make all of you regret it.}Nên là ngươi sẽ phải hối hận.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Now, use your magic.}Giờ thì sử dụng ma thuật đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can fall to your ruin\Nwith your own magical power...}Ngươi sẽ bị đánh bại bởi chính ma pháp của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{if you can even do...}Đó là nếu dám thi triển...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's...}{\i0}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's...}{\i0}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's...}{\i0}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's not magic!}{\i0}Đó có phải là ma thuật đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then, that time...}{\i0}Vậy lúc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And that time...}{\i0}Và lúc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And that time...}{\i0}Và cả lúc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And that time...}{\i0}Khi đó nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And that time...}{\i0}Và lúc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This, that, and just now!}{\i0}Khi đó, lúc nãy nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Y-You mean nothing until now was magic?}T-Từ đầu đến giờ không sử dụng ma thuật?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mash did everything with his body alone?}Mash là pháp sư hệ vật lý?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Seriously?}Đùa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{- That would be unbelievable.\N- Totally unbelievable, right?}Sao có thể chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That would be like something\Nout of a fantasy story.}Nghe cứ như truyện giả tưởng ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Like, exactly from a fantasy story.}Ừ thì truyện này giả tưởng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That sounds like a fantasy story.}Giả tưởng thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What? It didn't work against him at all!}Nó không ảnh hưởng tới Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Did this appear because I touched that kid?}{\i0}Nó xuất hiện vì mình chạm vào tên đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That headache earlier, too.}{\i0}Cơn đau đầu khi nãy nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So he really is...}{\i0}Vậy ra nó đúng là...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What is that?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Today was surprisingly productive\Nthanks to meeting you.}Hôm nay thật nhiều\N chuyện thú vị nhờ gặp được ngươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{My name is Cell War.}Tên ta là Cell War.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.47,Default,On-screen text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{INNOCENT ZERO\NCELL WAR}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I remembered I had an urgent errand,\Nso I'll be going now.}Tự nhiên có việc gấp nên ta về đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But we'll be seeing each other again soon.}Nhưng chúng ta sẽ gặp nhau sớm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Bye-bye.}Chào nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you're going home,\NI'm thankful that you're going home.}Nếu muốn về thì về luôn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Now, let's take Mask Guy\Nto the infirmary.}Giờ thì đưa anh Mặt nạ đến bệnh viên thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You don't have to worry about that.}Không cần phải lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thanks to the handkerchief you gave him,\Nit looks like things won't be too serious.}Nhờ khăn tay cầm máu nên\N có vẻ không quá nghiêm trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{P-Please treat me...\Nto cream puffs next time.}L-Lần tới... nhớ đãi tôi bánh su kem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mask Guy.}Anh mặt nạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I will take responsibility\Nand take Abyss back.}Ta sẽ chịu trách nhiệm chữa cho Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I give you my thanks,\NMash Burnedead.}Cảm ơn cậu, Mash Burnedead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I will make sure to return the favor.}Ta sẽ trả lại ơn nghĩa lần này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I guess that settles it.}Vậy là giải quyết xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait, hold up!}Có cái đầu mày ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Whaddaya mean,\Nnone of that was magic!?}Từ trước đến giờ không phải ma pháp à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's actually amazing,\Nbut isn't it terrible if people found out?}Tuy là quá đỉnh nhưng bị lộ là tiêu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's terrible, Mash! Being expelled\Nmight not be the end of it!}Nguy lắm đó. Cậu sẽ bị đuổi học ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{N-N-N-N-No-No-No, I-I-I-I c-c-can use m-m-m-magic-c-c-c-c-c-c-c...}K-K-K-Không, đ-đ-đó l-l-là m-m-ma t-t-thuật...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:10.56,Default,On-screen text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{TREMBLE TREMBLE TREMBLE}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's losing it!}Đang run rẩy kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He must have a really important reason.}Hẳn phải có lý do nào đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Anyway, we've gotta protect Mash's secret\Nso people won't find out.}Cơ mà chúng ta sẽ giữ bí mật cho Mash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right!}Phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If Mash's record gets tarnished,\Nit'll affect our married life, too.}Nếu Mash bị gì thì sẽ\N ảnh hưởng đến hôn nhân của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Anyway, we can shelter Mash for now,\Nat least until we figure out a plan.}Tóm lại là giữ bí mật rồi tìm cách giải quyết sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thanks, guys.}Cảm ơn mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He just said "thanks"!}Cậu ấy nói cảm ơn kìa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I wasn't expecting him\Nto acknowledge everything.}Vậy là thừa nhận sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But this is turning into a hell of a mess.}Nhưng vụ này sẽ thành một mớ hỗn độn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If they find out we're protecting Mash's secret,\Nwe'll definitely be in trouble, too.}Nếu bị lộ ra, chúng ta chắc chắn cũng đi theo Mash đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We might be expelled, too.}Cả đám sẽ bị đuổi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I heard everything!}Tao đã nghe hết rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A student who can't use magic in our school?\NThat's an outrage!}Học sinh không dùng được ma pháp? Vụ này quá lớn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm telling the teachers!}Tao sẽ báo thầy cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We're in trouble!}Chúng ta tiêu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The students who were turned into puppets...}Những học sinh bị biến thành rối...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{They had woken up!}Đã tỉnh dậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A student at a magic school can't use magic?}Học sinh trường ma pháp không dùng được ma thuật?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Report him! Report, report, report!}Phải báo cáo! Báo cáo! Báo cáo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:09.49,Default,On-screen text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{HONK}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This time has finally come.}Cuối cùng cũng đến lúc này...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's not phased at all!}{\i0}Hoàn toàn không phản kháng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{People have finally caught on\Nto Mash's inability to use magic.}{\i0}Mọi người cuối cùng cũng \Nbiết Mash không có phép thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What will you do, Mash!?}{\i0}Làm sao đây Mash?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:29.01,Default,On-screen text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{NOM NOM NOM}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This puts a hard stop on a happy life\Ntogether with your Pops!}{\i0}Điều này sẽ cản trở cuộc sống \Nyên bình của cậu với ông già .
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Father.}Thưa cha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{My apologies for taking so much time.}Xin lỗi vì đã mất nhiều thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But I have found it. What was lost.}Nhưng con đã tìm thấy. Thứ bị mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see. At last...}Vậy à. Cuối cùng...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{At last, my most earnest wish will come true.}Thì mong ước to lớn của ta đã thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Go retrieve it.}Bắt nó về.
